[src:abortion-in-south-carolina/abortion-in-alaska] In 2022, there were three Planned Parenthood clinics in the state.
[src:abortion-in-south-carolina/abortion-in-alaska] In 2024, there were two Planned Parenthood clinics.
[src:abortion-in-south-carolina/abortion-in-alaska] In 1990, 69,000 women in the state faced the risk of an unintended pregnancy.
